  <brief_title>Effect of Antiseizure Medication on Hormone Levels and Sexual Function in Men With Epilepsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Antiseizure Medication-Induced Elevation of Serum Estradiol and Reproductive Dysfunction in Men With Epilepsy</official_title>
