  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Must be a male between 18-50 years of age

          -  Must have seizures

          -  Must be on antiseizure medication for at least six months duration

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Must not have taken hormones, major tranquilizers or antidepressants for at least 3
             months
      </textblock>
